data.title: Almighty Military Format
data.meta_description: Almighty Military Format - Free download as Text File (.txt), PDF File (.pdf) or read online for free. The document appears to be messages between two individuals. The messages discuss getting to know each other better by asking questions about likes/dislikes, hobbies, and background details. However, some details raise suspicions, such as claiming to be stationed in Syria but also mentioning being in the US and having a daughter. The individual provides inconsistent stories about their family and military service.
